short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: It is used to import product from AliExpress to magento store and it can be used with webkul magento2 dropship management module.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Magento 2 Aliexpress Importer will import products of Aliexpress to your Magento 2 store and can start selling those products within his own store very easily.
